Decisions
---------
- Adopt Charm v2 (the design doc's v1 snippets predated v2 GA); v2 modules import
  from charm.land, not github.com/charmbracelet.
- Relative age is precomputed at SetItems time, not per render; it is frozen while
  the TUI is open (deliberate trade-off; refresh later on the SetItems path, never
  in the hot Render path).
- runTUI split into testable buildTUI + launch, with injectable ProgramOptions so
  the launch path is covered headlessly.
- Filter/search, m/M read toggles, open-in-browser, and the background sync engine
  remain deferred (steps 05/07).
